Pig Jam Committee
The Plant City Pig Jam is organized by staff and a committee of volunteers of the Plant City Chamber.
The committee meets regularly throughout the year to plan.
You can meet the people behind the pigs by volunteering at the Annual Plant City Pig Jam!
